# Azure Deployment Plan for modaia-closet Project

## Goal
Desplegar la plataforma en Azure con AZ CLI, IaC Bicep y CI/CD en GitHub Actions.

## Project Information
- AppName: modaia-closet
- Stack: Next.js 14 (web) + NestJS (api) + PostgreSQL + Redis
- Type: SaaS/Ecommerce con modulos de IA de medicion y recomendacion de talla
- Hosting: Azure App Service Linux para web y api
- Data: Azure Database for PostgreSQL Flexible Server + Azure Cache for Redis
- AI: Azure OpenAI + Azure AI Services (Vision)

## Azure Resources Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
svcweb["web Next.js"] --> appweb["Azure App Service Web"]
svcapi["api NestJS"] --> appapi["Azure App Service API"]
appweb -->|HTTPS| appapi
appapi --> pg["Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server"]
appapi --> redis["Azure Cache for Redis"]
appapi --> kv["Azure Key Vault"]
appapi --> blob["Azure Storage Blob"]
appapi --> openai["Azure OpenAI"]
appapi --> vision["Azure AI Vision"]
appweb --> cdn["Azure Front Door/CDN"]
appweb --> appinsights["Application Insights"]
appapi --> appinsights
```

- El frontend consume la API por HTTPS.
- La API concentra acceso a datos, IA y secretos.
- Key Vault almacena secretos de DB, JWT y terceros.
- App Insights unifica telemetria de web/api.

## Recommended Azure Resources
- Compute:
  - Azure App Service Plan Linux PremiumV3 P1v3 (autoscaling recomendado para produccion)
  - Azure App Service Web (Node 20)
  - Azure App Service API (Node 20)
- Data:
  - Azure Database for PostgreSQL Flexible Server General Purpose (2 vCPU minimo)
  - Azure Cache for Redis Standard C1
- Storage:
  - Azure Storage Account (Blob para imagenes/video360/avatars)
- Security and secrets:
  - Azure Key Vault Standard
  - Managed Identity para apps
- Observability:
  - Log Analytics + Application Insights
- AI:
  - Azure OpenAI (chatbot/personal shopper)
  - Azure AI Services Vision (analitica visual)

## Recommended Security Configurations
- Managed Identity para API/Web y acceso sin llaves hardcodeadas.
- Secretos sensibles en Key Vault.
- HTTPS only, TLS 1.2+, cabeceras seguras y rate limiting.
- Integrar Front Door WAF para produccion.

## Execution Steps
- [x] Crear IaC base en `infra/main.bicep`.
- [x] Crear pipelines CI/CD (`.github/workflows/deploy-azure-appservice.yml`, `azure-pipelines.yml`).
- [ ] Definir subscription y resource group de destino.
- [ ] Provisionar recursos con `az deployment group create`.
- [ ] Configurar secretos/variables del repo y App Services.
- [ ] Ejecutar despliegue y validar logs.

